---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About Zita">
  <main>
    <h1>Get to know <span class="text-gradient">Zita</span></h1>
    <p class="instructions">
      Zita, the Czech coding sensation, can debug a program with one hand tied
      behind her back, all while sipping on a cup of absinthe.
    </p>
    <p class="instructions">
      Her code is so clean, it once brought a tear to an old compiler's eye, who
      never thought it would witness such elegance.
    </p>
    <p class="instructions">
      Rumor has it that Zita's keyboard has a secret admiration mode that
      activates whenever she starts typing â€“ even the most stoic lines of code
      can't help but blush.
    </p>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  main {
    margin: auto;
    padding: 1rem;
    width: 800px;
    max-width: calc(100% - 2rem);
    color: white;
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: 4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1em;
  }
  .text-gradient {
    background-image: var(--accent-gradient);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-size: 400%;
    background-position: 0%;
  }
  .instructions {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(var(--accent-light), 25%);
    background: linear-gradient(
      rgba(var(--accent-dark), 66%),
      rgba(var(--accent-dark), 33%)
    );
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }
</style>
